Object.Field: Complex mapping to map multiple source tables to single PRODUCT target table.
LKM Oracle to Oracle Pull (DB Link)
CASE WHEN @{R0} = 1 THEN 1 WHEN @{R1} = 1 THEN 2 ELSE 3 END
CASE WHEN CATALOGUE.DIRECT = 1 THEN 1 WHEN CATALOGUE.BLUE_DIAMOND = 1 THEN 2 ELSE 3 END
CASE WHEN SUBSTR(@{R0},1,2)='GH' THEN 'HA' ELSE SUBSTR(@{R0},1,1) END
CASE WHEN SUBSTR(CATALOGUE.NPC,1,2)='GH' THEN 'HA' ELSE SUBSTR(CATALOGUE.NPC,1,1) END
@{R0} NOT LIKE 'N%' AND @{R0} NOT LIKE 'X%' AND @{R1}=901 AND @{R2} = 'N'
CATALOGUE.NPC NOT LIKE 'N%' AND CATALOGUE.NPC NOT LIKE 'X%' AND NPC_STOCK.WHSE_CODE=901 AND NPC_STOCK.VAT_EXEMPT_YN = 'N'
